<div class="accordion-wrapper js_accordion accordion-expanded content"
     data-desktop="closed"
     data-mobile="closed"
     data-tablet="closed">
    
        
            
            
                <div tabindex="0" class="accordion-clickable js_accordion-clickable accordion-plus">
                    
                    <span class="accordion-text"><p class="heading">我可以使用差價合約來進行石油交易嗎？</p>
</span>
                </div>
            
        
    
    
    <div class="accordion-parsys js_accordion_content accordion-content accordion-parsys parsys">
<!-- DBG: included_as_snippet=false -->
<div class="rich-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            text-layout-full-left
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            text-no-image
            imagesize50
            
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        <div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
    
        
    



                





        <p>可以。買賣單個石油差價合約等同於購買單個石油期貨。例如，購買一個布倫特原油差價合約等同於在基礎市場中購買1000桶原油。</p>

<p>您可以對一個合約的一部分進行交易，從而限制您的風險敞口，而且您可以在市場下跌和上漲兩個方向上進行投資。詳細了解<a href="/cn/cfd-trading">差價合約交易</a>。</p>


                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
